Source.Name: qgis
Source.Summary: A Free and Open Source Geographic Information System
Source.Description: QGIS is a professional GIS application that is built on top of and proud to be itself Free and Open Source Software (FOSS). Create, edit, visualise, analyse and publish geospatial information on Windows, Mac, Linux, BSD (Android coming soon).
